---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.astro";
---

<Layout title="Servizi e Tariffe - Rocco Andrea Ligorio">
    <Navigation />

    <div class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50">
        <main class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-20">
            <!-- Header -->
            <header class="mb-20 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <h1
                    class="font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-6"
                >
                    Servizi Tech
                </h1>
                <p
                    class="font-medium text-lg md:text-xl text-blue-600 mb-8 inline-block"
                >
                    Soluzioni informatiche chiare, con prezzi comprensibili.
                </p>
                <div
                    class="prose prose-lg mx-auto text-slate-600 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    <p>
                        L’informatica non è magia nera, è logica applicata. Qui
                        non trovi marketing gonfiato o promesse da marinaio.
                        Trovi un approccio pratico: analizzo il problema, ti
                        spiego come risolverlo in italiano (non in "tecnichese")
                        e ti do un'idea chiara dei costi prima di iniziare. La
                        trasparenza è l'unica "feature" che non è opzionale.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </header>

            <div
                class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-20"
            >
                <!-- 1. Assistenza informatica -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 font-bold text-6xl text-slate-900 select-none pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity"
                    >
                        01
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-4 pr-8 uppercase tracking-wide"
                    >
                        Assistenza Informatica
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                        Supporto pratico per PC e sistemi Windows. Dal computer
                        lento che ti fa disperare ai problemi di configurazione
                        post-aggiornamento.
                    </p>
                    <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <span
                            class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-slate-400 block mb-1 tracking-wider"
                            >Tariffa base</span
                        >
                        <div class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-900">
                            a partire da <span
                                class="text-blue-600 text-xl ml-1"
                                >35 €/ora</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 2. Supporto remoto -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 font-bold text-6xl text-slate-900 select-none pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity"
                    >
                        02
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-4 pr-8 uppercase tracking-wide"
                    >
                        Supporto Remoto
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                        Interventi rapidi a distanza. Mi collego, ti spiego cosa
                        sto facendo e risolvo. Ideale per urgenze che non
                        richiedono un cacciavite.
                    </p>
                    <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <span
                            class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-slate-400 block mb-1 tracking-wider"
                            >Tariffa base</span
                        >
                        <div class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-900">
                            a partire da <span
                                class="text-blue-600 text-xl ml-1"
                                >35 €/ora</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 3. Consulenza informatica -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 font-bold text-6xl text-slate-900 select-none pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity"
                    >
                        03
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-4 pr-8 uppercase tracking-wide"
                    >
                        Consulenza
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                        Devi comprare hardware, software o scegliere un cloud?
                        Ti aiuto a spendere bene i tuoi soldi, evitando
                        soluzioni sovradimensionate.
                    </p>
                    <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <span
                            class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-slate-400 block mb-1 tracking-wider"
                            >Tariffa base</span
                        >
                        <div class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-900">
                            a partire da <span
                                class="text-blue-600 text-xl ml-1"
                                >60 €/ora</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 4. Seconda opinione -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 font-bold text-6xl text-slate-900 select-none pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity"
                    >
                        04
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-4 pr-8 uppercase tracking-wide"
                    >
                        Seconda Opinione
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                        Hai un preventivo che non ti convince? Un progetto IT
                        che sembra fumoso? Analizzo la situazione e ti do un
                        parere indipendente e disinteressato.
                    </p>
                    <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <span
                            class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-slate-400 block mb-1 tracking-wider"
                            >Analisi</span
                        >
                        <div class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-900">
                            a partire da <span
                                class="text-blue-600 text-xl ml-1">70 €</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 5. Siti Internet -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 font-bold text-6xl text-slate-900 select-none pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity"
                    >
                        05
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-4 pr-8 uppercase tracking-wide"
                    >
                        Siti Internet
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                        Siti web semplici, chiari e veloci. Niente effetti
                        speciali inutili, solo quello che serve per presentarti
                        online in modo professionale.
                    </p>
                    <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <span
                            class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-slate-400 block mb-1 tracking-wider"
                            >Progetto</span
                        >
                        <div class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-900">
                            a partire da <span
                                class="text-blue-600 text-xl ml-1">600 €</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 6. Web App -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 font-bold text-6xl text-slate-900 select-none pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity"
                    >
                        06
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-4 pr-8 uppercase tracking-wide"
                    >
                        Web App
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                        Mini gestionali, dashboard di controllo, strumenti per
                        uso interno. Software cucito sulle tue esigenze, non
                        pacchetti standard dove usi il 10%.
                    </p>
                    <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <span
                            class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-slate-400 block mb-1 tracking-wider"
                            >Sviluppo</span
                        >
                        <div class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-900">
                            a partire da <span
                                class="text-blue-600 text-xl ml-1">900 €</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 7. Automazioni -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 font-bold text-6xl text-slate-900 select-none pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity"
                    >
                        07
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-4 pr-8 uppercase tracking-wide"
                    >
                        Automazioni
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                        Fai sempre gli stessi clic? Copi-incolli dati a mano?
                        Creiamo script e flussi che fanno il lavoro noioso al
                        posto tuo.
                    </p>
                    <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <span
                            class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-slate-400 block mb-1 tracking-wider"
                            >Setup</span
                        >
                        <div class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-900">
                            a partire da <span
                                class="text-blue-600 text-xl ml-1"
                                >50 €/ora</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 8. Backup Reale -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 font-bold text-6xl text-slate-900 select-none pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity"
                    >
                        08
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-4 pr-8 uppercase tracking-wide"
                    >
                        Backup Reale
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                        Un backup non testato è solo una speranza. Configuro
                        sistemi di salvataggio (locali e cloud) e verifico che i
                        dati si possano recuperare davvero.
                    </p>
                    <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <span
                            class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-slate-400 block mb-1 tracking-wider"
                            >Configurazione</span
                        >
                        <div class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-900">
                            a partire da <span
                                class="text-blue-600 text-xl ml-1">100 €</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 9. Sicurezza Base -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 font-bold text-6xl text-slate-900 select-none pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity"
                    >
                        09
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-4 pr-8 uppercase tracking-wide"
                    >
                        Sicurezza Base
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                        Nessun sistema è inespugnabile, ma non lasciamo la porta
                        aperta. Password manager, 2FA, e buone pratiche per
                        dormire sonni tranquilli.
                    </p>
                    <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <span
                            class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-slate-400 block mb-1 tracking-wider"
                            >Intervento</span
                        >
                        <div class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-900">
                            a partire da <span
                                class="text-blue-600 text-xl ml-1">80 €</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 10. Formazione -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col group relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 font-bold text-6xl text-slate-900 select-none pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity"
                    >
                        10
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-4 pr-8 uppercase tracking-wide"
                    >
                        Formazione
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
                        Impara a usare i tuoi strumenti senza paura. Sessioni
                        personalizzate, mirate a quello che ti serve davvero
                        sapere. Zero teoria inutile.
                    </p>
                    <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <span
                            class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-slate-400 block mb-1 tracking-wider"
                            >Lezione</span
                        >
                        <div class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-900">
                            a partire da <span
                                class="text-blue-600 text-xl ml-1"
                                >50 €/ora</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 11. Help Desk -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 group relative overflow-hidden ring-4 ring-blue-50/50"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 font-bold text-6xl text-blue-900 select-none pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity"
                    >
                        11
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="font-bold text-xl text-blue-900 mb-4 pr-8 uppercase tracking-wide"
                    >
                        Help Desk
                    </h3>
                    <p
                        class="text-slate-700 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed font-medium"
                    >
                        Il tuo reparto IT in outsourcing. Un riferimento fisso
                        per la tua micro-azienda. Priorità di intervento e
                        monitoraggio costante.
                    </p>
                    <div class="border-t border-blue-100 pt-6 mt-auto">
                        <span
                            class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-blue-400 block mb-1 tracking-wider"
                            >Abbonamento</span
                        >
                        <div class="font-bold text-2xl text-blue-900">
                            a partire da <span
                                class="text-blue-600 text-xl ml-1"
                                >120 €/mese</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Footer Note -->
            <div
                class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center border-t border-slate-200 pt-8 mb-12"
            >
                <p class="text-slate-500 italic text-sm">
                    * I prezzi indicati sono orientativi e dipendono dalla
                    complessità reale del lavoro. Prima di proporre una
                    soluzione, viene sempre valutata la reale necessità tramite
                    preventivo gratuito.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 text-center">
                <a
                    href="/contatti"
                    class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold uppercase text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1 no-underline"
                >
                    Richiedi Preventivo
                </a>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>
</Layout>
